If all goes well,

83
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,780
I'll return to my post soon.

84
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,310
So, don't blame yourself too much.

85
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,440
Then, Mr. Shu,

86
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:52,300
