223
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:09,690
Sure, you go rest.

224
00:12:09,690 --> 00:12:10,990
- I'm leaving.
- I'm going to watch TV.

225
00:12:10,990 --> 00:12:11,800
Okay.

226
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:18,700
