259
00:14:00,040 --> 00:14:01,360
Take this Talisman.

260
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,580
It's for protection.

261
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:05,200
I'll go check outside.

262
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:07,100
Hold onto it tightly.

263
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,300
Don't be afraid.

264
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:11,580
