268
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:17,460
Fang Meng, I'm scared.

269
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:19,980
I'm scared.

270
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,560
Shh.

271
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,180
Ready?

272
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:33,640
Well,

273
00:14:34,280 --> 00:14:35,760
